  Instagram
  Facebook
  Display Ads
  Podcasting
  Viral
  Web site
  Online PR
  
ORGANIC SEO
  Search Engine Optimization is a montage of practices used to manipulate the search engines into giving you what you want.
PPC CAMPAIGNS
  Pay Per Clicks is a mechanism to hack your way up almost instantaneously You have to pay to get the results
  google adwords
CONTENT MARKETING
  Content caries context as it delivers message to the audience intended to elicit a desired response which is likely to make a sale out of them or make them promoters of your brand
  udk instagram fb postları....
INFLUENCER MARKETING
  Infographics are visual representations of data making complex info easier to share and digest.
  When making your owm, simply organize your images, charts and text. 
  Finaly, cite your sources
EMAIL MARKETING
